article_title: Wendy’s to Sell Another 500 Stores to Franchisees
article_text:
Wendy’s Co. unveiled plans on Tuesday to sell another 500 of its restaurants to franchisees as it seeks to cut down on spending.

The announcement came as Wendy’s also gave a disappointing outlook for 2015 and reported preliminary revenue for its fourth quarter that missed expectations.
